---
title: Mexican Spiced Salmon Roll with Sweet Potato Wedges and Charred Corn and Avocado Salsa
description: Fresh, satisfying, feel-good food is how we’d describe our mexican-spiced salmon roll. We’ve filled sweet, warm brioche rolls with zesty, spiced salmon and topped with harred sweetcorn, creamy avocado and tomato salsa for a true taste sensation.
